{"tid":138769,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點心皇前大股東不滿飛機延誤　訛稱行理有炸彈　裁定發假消息罪成","createTime":"2017-03-01T00:28:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-01T01:56:21.000Z","uid":73262,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"615ed7074f66f7fcc7c86b14a7ff319010ead4dc","tid":138769,"uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T00:28:03.000Z","msg":"連鎖式食肆「點心皇」前大股東馮偉開去年乘國泰航班往南韓首爾，惟航班臨起飛前因冷氣故障而兩度延遲，馮遂與空姐理論並要求落機，期間馮涉嫌揚言「寄艙行李我唔要喇，由得佢喺度，等佢爆炸」；又涉嫌向另一名空少「爆粗」，結果遭警員上機拘捕。馮早前不認罪受審，聲稱只稱「熱到爆炸」，今被裁定向他人傳達有炸彈的虛假消息罪成，案件押後至3月20日判刑，以待索閱背景及社會服務令報告。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/74913/%E9%BB%9E%E5%BF%83%E7%9A%87%E5%89%8D%E5%A4%A7%E8%82%A1%E6%9D%B1%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF%E9%A3%9B%E6%A9%9F%E5%BB%B6%E8%AA%A4-%E8%A8%9B%E7%A8%B1%E8%A1%8C%E7%90%86%E6%9C%89%E7%82%B8%E5%BD%88-%E8%A3%81%E5%AE%9A%E7%99%BC%E5%81%87%E6%B6%88%E6%81%%BD%AA%E6%88%90\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2F74913%2F%25E9%25BB%259E%25E5%25BF%2583%25E7%259A%2587%25E5%2589%258D%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%2582%25A1%25E6%259D%25B1%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25BB%25BF%25E9%25A3%259B%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%25BB%25B6%25E8%25AA%25A4-%25E8%25A8%259B%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E8%25A1%258C%25E7%2590%2586%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%2582%25B8%25E5%25BD%2588-%25E8%25A3%2581%25E5%25AE%259A%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%2581%2587%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590&d=RNMQoofY58y8BAaKNkwZNuargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=cae1ddfd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/74913/%E9%BB%9E%E5%BF%83%E7%9A%87%E5%89%8D%E5%A4%A7%E8%82%A1%E6%9D%B1%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF%E9%A3%9B%E6%A9%9F%E5%BB%B6%E8%AA%A4-%E8%A8%9B%E7%A8%B1%E8%A1%8C%E7%90%86%E6%9C%89%E7%82%B8%E5%BD%88-%E8%A3%81%E5%AE%9A%E7%99%BC%E5%81%87%E6%B6%88%E6%81%%BD%AA%E6%88%90</a>"},{"pid":"0dd89ad8ea9882a45b210a33ae1b53e0c559844e","tid":138769,"uid":5858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T01:39:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\"